    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>每一步都是风险。你能做到吗？</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在移动之前先三思。一旦你开始移动，你的视野就会受限，只有记忆和反应才能救你。在黑暗中，你的反应有多快？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055110/extras/844577454c186d6723ab5483b15d3eab.poster.avif?t=1772376838\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055110/extras/844577454c186d6723ab5483b15d3eab.webm?t=1772376838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055110/extras/844577454c186d6723ab5483b15d3eab.mp4?t=1772376838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>为所有人带来保证的乐趣</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从高手到休闲玩家，自由选择你的玩法，通过可自定义的难度选项调整体验。可在黑暗中调节视野范围，并探索更多无障碍设置。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055110/extras/1e2b7283caa17fcf0ff5c0b06e8aa341.poster.avif?t=1772376838\" width=780 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055110/extras/1e2b7283caa17fcf0ff5c0b06e8aa341.webm?t=1772376838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055110/extras/1e2b7283caa17fcf0ff5c0b06e8aa341.mp4?t=1772376838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>大胆迈出危险的大步</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一关你只有有限的光源。如果你频繁移动和停下，光源就会耗尽，剩下的关卡将完全陷入黑暗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055110/extras/f74b11d0d652739f9e685cdc7ce4c590.poster.avif?t=1772376838\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055110/extras/f74b11d0d652739f9e685cdc7ce4c590.webm?t=1772376838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055110/extras/f74b11d0d652739f9e685cdc7ce4c590.mp4?t=1772376838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>收集珍贵的水晶和宝石</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一颗水晶和宝石都有独特的挑战。只有最熟练的冒险者才能找到隐藏在黑暗中的所有失落宝藏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055110/extras/d0f947f4392fb099ddfadb7c13e7488c.poster.avif?t=1772376838\" width=780 height=310 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055110/extras/d0f947f4392fb099ddfadb7c13e7488c.webm?t=1772376838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055110/extras/d0f947f4392fb099ddfadb7c13e7488c.mp4?t=1772376838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>挑战史诗级的BOSS战</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dr. Fog 会不择手段让世界陷入黑暗。只有敏锐的反应、精准的操作和无畏的决心，才能让你击败他暗影般的盟友，并最终与他正面对决！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055110/extras/1306bde32c7668de39097dc522d56dc9.poster.avif?t=1772376838\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055110/extras/1306bde32c7668de39097dc522d56dc9.webm?t=1772376838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055110/extras/1306bde32c7668de39097dc522d56dc9.mp4?t=1772376838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关于开发者与这款游戏的诞生</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大家好，我是 Ramy！Light Dude 是我在 Steam 上的第一款游戏！整个游戏诞生于一次痛苦的经历……有一次我在黑暗中从浴室走回房间，自以为对房间的布局了如指掌……直到床架提醒了我事实并非如此……我的脚趾损失了99%的HP，但至少我解锁了一个新的游戏创意！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055110/extras/9a3d8ac078512a2bdc0d193b71eb92e5.poster.avif?t=1772376838\" width=780 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055110/extras/9a3d8ac078512a2bdc0d193b71eb92e5.webm?t=1772376838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055110/extras/9a3d8ac078512a2bdc0d193b71eb92e5.mp4?t=1772376838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
